name: 01 Memory Card - Opa Monk
description: If you are looking for rare items or used items of good quality, come to the Opa Monk shop! Opa Monk was an intelligent and well-respected mole with sharp eyes in El Dorado. It feels respected to talk to charismatic figures like Opa Monk. He is good at observing people's characters. His side job is as an information seller in Lucid City.
